The contents of this directory (deploy/) contain reference deployment
artifacts — Dockerfiles, a generic Helm chart, and example Kubernetes
manifests — licensed under the Apache License 2.0, overriding the
repository-wide AGPL-3.0-only default.

This permissive license allows self-hosters to derive their own production
infrastructure from these templates without AGPL obligations.

